{{Otheruses|Bender}}
A '''bender''' was a type of [[Droid/Legends|droid]] used in construction. Along with [[extruder]]s and [[Shaper (droid)|shapers]], benders made up part of the complement of droids used at [[Despayre]] to build the [[DS-1 Orbital Battle Station/Legends|Death Star I]].<ref name="Death Star">''[[Death Star (novel)|''Death Star'']]</ref>

